Sources: 
	1. JavaBrains  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-wDUChgvYgU
	2. https://spring.io/guides/gs/authenticating-ldap/  -- copied code from: Set up User Data 

How to run:
	1. http://localhost:8080/login
	2. enter credentials
		user name: ben
		password:  benspassword
		
Summary:		

In this project we've build our own ldap server and small API to validate login. In real project just connect to 
production LDAP server.  LdapShaPasswordEncoder() was deprecated and not recommended to use in production app.